            <title><![CDATA[[话筒]#怎样预防甲流和诺如病毒#？近期，多地中小学校因传染病而班级停课，宝爸宝妈很忧心！[抓狂][抓狂]春季细菌及病毒种类繁多，气温多变使得人体免疫力不稳定...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%BA%E5%A6%82%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%BA%E5%A6%82%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#怎样预防甲流和诺如病毒#</span></a>？<br><br>近期，多地中小学校因传染病而班级停课，宝爸宝妈很忧心！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>春季细菌及病毒种类繁多，气温多变使得人体免疫力不稳定等，易造成春季传染病高发。<br><br>与新冠感染一样，甲流、诺如病毒感染也会引起感冒、发热等症状。甲流和诺如病毒传播途径有何不同？感染后如何治疗？👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （人民日报）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hbdi3gw7xfj20u06jxnpd.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
